@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title Linear state machine (v2) — 4 statuses + label signals\n(transition = trigger + model)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EAF3FF
  BorderColor #336699
  FontName Helvetica
}

[*] --> Todo

Todo --> Todo : DEV asks @Mateusz\n(needs:answer, PL · MiniMax M3)
Todo --> InProgress : plan approved (emoji V)\n(HITL · GLM-5.2)
Todo --> Canceled : dropped
InProgress --> InReview : code done + DoD + checklist\n(ai:coded · GLM-5.2)
InProgress --> InProgress : checkpoint -> STATE.md
InReview --> InProgress : changes requested\n(Conventional Comments · round++)
InReview --> Done : review clean + tests pass\n(ai:reviewed · GLM-5.2 deep + DeepSeek V4 Pro)
Done --> [*]

state InReview {
  [*] --> Reviewing
  Reviewing --> Testing : approve (stage:testing)
  Testing --> [*] : deploy+tests pass
  Testing --> Reviewing : retest
}

note right of Todo
  Entry gate = dor-ok flag
  (Why/AC/scope-out/deps).
  type:spike -> ADR, skips deploy.
end note

note right of InReview
  Max 2 dev<->review rounds,
  then escalated -> @Mateusz.
  Testing = deploy GCP (OpenRouter)
  with health-check + rollback;
  Ollama/GPU -> Lambda AI.
end note

note bottom of InProgress
  Flags any state: needs:* ·
  blocked · risk:high ·
  escalated · over-budget.
end note
@enduml
